Class ClarInfoAndFiles

public class ClarInfoAndFiles
extends RunInfoAndFiles

A single clarification (info)

Contains clar information (siteId, runId, problem info, language info, elapsed time (minutes), team info, whether the problem was solved, and other settings)

Inheirits from RunInfoAndFiles, has three more fields: Question and Answer and SendToAllTeams

It is assumes that a clar is not answered if getAnswer() returns null or empty string.
